The Spokesperson of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs on Monday condoled the death of the legendary right winger, hockey World Cup winner, and captain of Team Pakistan Manzoor Hussain Junior.
In a tweet, he said, “Adieu #ManzoorHussain Junior legendary right winger, Olympian, World Cup winner & captain of Team Pakistan that won Hockey Gold at 1984 LA Olympics.”
